small-batch-sentences-rule-3 = Separe fraz  an  sèl liy appuyé asou "Antre" oubyen "Retounen" yon fwa.
small-batch-sentences-rule-4 = Ajoute jiska 1,000 fraz
small-batch-sentences-rule-5 = Tout fraz dwet ni menm domèn an.
small-batch-sentences-rule-6 = Tout fraz  dwet ni menm sitasyon an.
